description: Georgia has recorded fewer than 1,000 infections and only 15 deaths among its 3.7 million people.
title: Coronavirus: How 'three musketeers' helped Georgia fight virus
title_page: Coronavirus: How 'three musketeers' helped Georgia fight virus - BBC News
maintext: "We decided to live with the virus regardless of the numbers. We don't have an end goal to eradicate it. Because it is impossible. If we have to close borders for a year, close businesses for months and years we will die from other causes."
